GAS TRANSPORTATION REPORT via NewsNet
NOVEMBER 2, 1994

Futures

      December futures will find technical support at around $1.93,
with short covering expecting at that level, said an analyst.
However, the contract is expected to find its ceiling at $1.87 and
then trade lower.




