RANGE OF REPORTED SPOT PRICES (DEC. 1, 1995, ISSUE)

The ``Range of reported spot prices'' for California published in the Dec.
1, 1995, issue did not reflect the full range of the individual California
line items. The correct range is $1.39 to $1.73.

