ATIC Services has appointed Thierry Arnold as chairman, replacing
Pierre Verbrugghe. Michel Margnes has been reappointed as president,
Michel Bellissant as CEO and Gilbert Join as secretary.  ATIC Services
was set up early last year when the ATIC's monopoly for coal imports
into France was abolished.



