TIGAZ BOARD BACKS $280M PLAN

A board meeting of Hungarian utility Tigaz, whose control was recently
acquired by Italy's Italgas and Snam (IGR 289/4 and see separate
story), has named Eugenio Lancellotta as chairman and approved a five
