Canada - Atco Ltd is negotiating sale of subsidiary Atcor Resources to
an unnamed buyer. Expected to fetch up to C$150m ($110m), Atcor has
reserves of 132 Bcf of gas and 13m bbls of oil, producing 46 MMcfd and
4,100 b/d respectively.



