MCN BUYING CONSOL COAL'S COALBED-METHANE BUSINESS

USA - MCN Corp is buying the Virginia assets of Consol Coal's coalbed-
methane business, including 130 wells, 80 miles of gathering line, a
50% stake in a 40 mile export line and 100,000 acres of methane
development land.

Cost of $120m covers reserves put at 250 Bcf proved, 250 Bcf probable
and potential, and 1.9m bbls of oil.



