JANUARY 16, 1995

ENERGY:  UP-TO-DATE OPEC PRODUCTION AND SUPPLY DATA -- DEC. 1994

   VIENNA, Jan. 16 (OPECNA) -- Production and supply data for the
month of December 1994 received to-date by the OPEC Secretariat
from member countries is as follows (in 1,000 b/d):

COUNTRY           PRODUCTION           SUPPLY
-------           ----------           ------

Algeria             751.0                750.0
Indonesia         1,328.9              1,329.8
Iran              3,595.0              3,595.0
Iraq                775.0                775.0
Kuwait            2,007.2              2,005.3
Libya             1,393.0              1,403.0
Nigeria           1,785.6              1,860.5
Qatar               381.3                378.9
Saudi Arabia      8,246.3              8,000.0
UAE               2,192.7              2,190.3
Venezuela         2,396.0              2,371.2

   Supply, as defined by OPEC, is calculated as domestic
consumption, plus net export sales of crude and products, plus
withdrawals of stocks held outside national boundaries.



