were perceived as tight. A refiner reportedly offered 50,000 bbl for
January 10-15 at 92.75 cts, FOB US Gulf. A producer indicated selling
interest for second half January at 93 cts, FOB US Gulf.
   In the Northeast, buying interest was again reported at close to 100 cts
in New York Harbor.

